title: Obama Dope rounded case for Iphone 5 with buttons

description.text: For the Obama fans under us

The stencil cut-out looks even better if a black paper is put between the Iphone and the case  
Instructions from BrandonW6:  
While not a direct derivative, I liked the case Helmi74 created and I wanted to add a few features. I recreated the case from scratch and added buttons on the outside. Also the front and back edges are rounded, which I think makes it a bit more comfortable to hold.   
After printing, take a fine hobby knife and clear out any threads that my interfere with the button clearance. Rub some sandpaper around any sharp edges, and give it a good cleaning to remove dust and debris.  
Pop in your Iphone 5 and enjoy!

description.text:
This is a remix of http://www.thingiverse.com/thing:145567
I have changed it a bit to fit my muddyfox bag.
The clip will hold a 10mm pipe and the strap slot is 32mm long and 2mm wide,with the return on the end it can be slid over the strap and is very unlikely to come off.
The clip is 10mm wide and I printed mine in PLA and has a good amount of flex in it to get over the strap.

I printed mine at 0.2 layer height and 40% fill in white PLA and it came out nice and has enough flex to get over a thicker strap.
Print and get running :)
fits in fillament spool. inside hole 22mm
